{
  "stem": "7938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This liquidation took one day, not a whole day even.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, the Jewish policemen were also there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They tried to help whatever the could, if somebody wanted to help, but it was not-- it was very difficult to do it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They stayed there, because they liquidated-- they still went through this whole thing for-- for-- for more than a week, to see whether nobody was hiding in the cellars or everything.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They couldn't do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first day they just do the rough job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the rest was-- the rest everything was done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this, we were saved.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And whatever-- whatever stories I would tell about the atrocities and everything-- [DOORBELL RINGING] Whatever atrocities-- [PAUSES FOR 12 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whatever atrocities-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] whatever atrocities they-- they were shown, I can give an account of it, will not be the same as what it really was.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's impossible to describe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is in Polish a saying of a famous poet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SPEAKING POLISH]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because this means in-- in translation--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the translation language.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In a translation language, it means that the tongue doesn't-- the language doesn't express your-- your voice, and the voice is not an expression of your mind.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think that-- that after, one of the-- of the writers of the Holocaust wrote-- wrote later on after the war, that no matter what we tell you, there is a line over which you cannot cross.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So whatever I will have to say about these things will just be, that's why this-- this-- I think that this is the value of the-- of the film, because if future generation will have to read it, it would be just something written, and-- and nothing will show up.",
      "word_count": 50
    }
  ],
